{"id":"acts-of-solomon","term":"Acts Of Solomon","source":"International Standard Bible Encyclopaedia (James Orr ed., 1915)","html":"<p>\"The book of the acts of Solomon\" (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 11:41\">1Ki 11:41</a>), probably a history based on the state documents kept by the official recorder. See <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 14:19\">1Ki 14:19</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 14:29\">29</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 15:23\">15:23</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 15:31\">31</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 16:5\">16:5</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 16:14\">14</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 16:20\">20</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 16:27\">27</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 22:39\">22:39</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 22:45\">45</a>, etc.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Kings 11:41","1 Kings 14:19","1 Kings 14:29","1 Kings 15:23","1 Kings 15:31","1 Kings 16:5","1 Kings 16:14","1 Kings 16:20","1 Kings 16:27","1 Kings 22:39","1 Kings 22:45"]}